title: ICE when compile redis on the last nightly

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
### Code

https://github.com/teloxide/teloxide/pull/335/checks?check_run_id=1801759422#step:4:650

### Meta
```
rustc 1.51.0-nightly (04caa632d 2021-01-30) running on x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu
```

### Error output

